kahawai
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:
Definition:an Australasian marine food fish, Arripis trutta, resembling salmon (also called (native or sea) salmon, sea trout).
Origin: Maori
Register:
Register 2:
Domain: [none]
Region: [none]
See:
Pronunciation:
